section.auth
  .container
    .page-header
      h1 #[span.fa.fa-sign-in] Login #[small Evernote Tasklog]
    .row
      .col-md-4
        button.btn.btn-default.btn-lg.btn-block(type="button", @click="login(false, false)") #[span.fa.fa-4x.fa-sign-in] #[br] Basic Login
      .col-md-8
        p: .well Login to system using the Evernote server authentication.
    hr
    .row
      .col-md-4
        button.btn.btn-default.btn-lg.btn-block(type="button", @click="login(false, true)", :disabled="!(authService.production && authService.production.token)") #[span.fa.fa-4x.fa-key] #[br] Token Login
        button.btn.btn-primary.btn-block(type="button", @click="setToken(false)") Set token #[br] (User: {{authService.production ? authService.production.username : 'none'}})
      .col-md-8
        p: .well Login to system using the Evernote developer token. Get token from&nbsp;
          a(href='https://www.evernote.com/api/DeveloperToken.action') Evernote developer token API
          br
          | Notice: All client in this server use this token.
    hr
    button.btn.btn-default.btn-block(type="button", @click="isDeveloper = !isDeveloper") Toggle Developer Mode
    div(v-if="isDeveloper")
      hr
      .row
        .col-md-4
          button.btn.btn-default.btn-lg.btn-block(type="button", @click="login(true, false)") #[span.fa.fa-4x.fa-sign-in] #[br] Sandbox Login
        .col-md-8
          p: .well Login to sandbox system using the Evernote sandbox server authentication.
      hr
      .row
        .col-md-4
          button.btn.btn-default.btn-lg.btn-block(type="button", @click="login(true, true)", :disabled="!(authService.sandbox && authService.sandbox.token)") #[span.fa.fa-4x.fa-key] #[br] Sandbox Token Login
          button.btn.btn-primary.btn-block(type="button", @click="setToken(true)") Set token #[br] (User: {{authService.sandbox ? authService.sandbox.username : "none"}})
        .col-md-8
          p: .well Login to sandbox system using the Evernote sandbox developer token. Get token from&nbsp;
            a(href="https://sandbox.evernote.com/api/DeveloperToken.action") Evernote sandbox developer token API
            br
            | Notice: All client in this server use this token.
